My name is Victor and I'm an owner of this site! I am a web developer with over 14 years of experience in front-end and back-end: theming, module and plugin development for Drupal and WordPress sites.

   I have solutions for small and middle businesses, community portals, e-commerce, and presentation websites. It is important to me to build long-term relationships with clients.
